This ·<193>ntimantra belongs to the <185>ukla Yajurveda.
It is quite enigmatic.
According to the Advaita Ved<193>nta, this universe is only a false ç
appearance in Brahman due to ignorance, even as a snake is seen in ç
a rope in semi-darkness.
When the rope is seen as rope in full light, it is `full'.
